com.iland.core.api.vcd

Class VappStartupSectionItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.iland.core.api.vcd.VappStartupSectionItem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class VappStartupSectionItem
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Vapp Startup Section Item Impl. Holds startup information for an individual Vm. The information is used at the Vapp level to determine Vm startup order as well as actions to take when Vapp is started / stopped.
    Author:
    Brett Snyder
